data.description: Come take a look at this recently renovated cute bungalow.  This home has a brand-new bathroom, kitchen and new flooring through-out the home. This home features neutral colors, large back-yard and partially finished basement equipped with a wet bar, a half bath and a fireplace. Property has already passed occupancy inspection. Move-in ready! Come take a look!
